{
  "stem": "22004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know the second name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know one name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first name it was Fischel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fischel, his name.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was with a long beard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a  young man with a long beard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was hiding between the Christians there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So someone was protecting him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Protecting, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They protect him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, finally we find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally we talk to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he knew my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He knew me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was with him working in a shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ukrainians and friends-- his friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He lived there, he was born there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, he said, if you are staying, they announced the Germans, all the men to come in the-- in the playground.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are going to send them away in a safe place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father was from the first, all the men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They make him to take off their clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Put it away in the side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they make him to dig a big trough all the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they make him to stand up naked by the grave and they shoot him in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did this Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fischel see this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he saw it because he was-- he was hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was between the-- Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they-- they shoot them, all the men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a big city with Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was a nice couple thousand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, they shoot all the men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then a couple days later, they called-- they put it in papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Announced, the wives and the children of the men to come in that-- in that playground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to send them to their mens, their husbands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was so tricky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, my sisters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they make them to dig a separate grave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was three graves there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
